ZH: 我收到了一封重要的邮件，请查看你的邮箱。
EN: I received an important email, please check your mailbox.

ZH: 请记得定期清理你的邮箱，以免遗漏重要信息。
EN: Please remember to clean out your mailbox regularly to avoid missing important information.

ZH: 我的邮箱容量快要满了，我需要清理一些邮件。
EN: My mailbox is almost full, I need to clear out some emails.

ZH: 许多公司都会通过邮箱发送工作相关的通知和文件。
EN: Many companies send work-related notifications and documents through email.

ZH: 请确保你的邮箱是安全的，以保护个人信息不被盗取。
EN: Please make sure your mailbox is secure to protect personal information from being stolen.

ZH: 昨天我把重要文件发到你的邮箱，请查收。
EN: I sent important documents to your mailbox yesterday, please check.

ZH: 我的邮箱里收到了一封来自未知发件人的邮件。
EN: I received an email from an unknown sender in my mailbox.

ZH: 我每天都会检查我的邮箱，以确保不错过任何消息。
EN: I check my mailbox every day to make sure I don't miss any messages.

ZH: 请不要随意泄露你的邮箱密码，以免被黑客入侵。
EN: Please do not disclose your mailbox password casually to avoid being hacked.

ZH: 你可以在我的邮箱中找到最新版本的文件。
EN: You can find the latest version of the file in my mailbox.

ZH: 请检查你的垃圾邮箱，有时重要邮件会被误分类。
EN: Please check your spam mailbox, sometimes important emails are misclassified.

ZH: 我的邮箱被黑客入侵了，所有的邮件都被删除了。
EN: My mailbox was hacked and all emails were deleted.

ZH: 我无法登录我的邮箱，可能是密码不正确。
EN: I can't log into my mailbox, it might be because of the incorrect password.

ZH: 我的邮箱收到了很多广告邮件，怎么办？
EN: My mailbox received a lot of spam emails, what should I do?

ZH: 请将需要备份的文件发送至我的邮箱。
EN: Please send the files that need to be backed up to my mailbox.

ZH: 我们公司的邮箱系统发生了故障，暂时无法正常收发邮件。
EN: Our company's mailbox system has malfunctioned and we are unable to send or receive emails temporarily.

ZH: 我的邮箱里有一封来自老板的紧急通知。
EN: There is an urgent notice from the boss in my mailbox.

ZH: 请确认你的电子邮件地址是否正确，以免邮件发送错误。
EN: Please confirm that your email address is correct to avoid sending emails to the wrong recipient.

ZH: 我通过邮箱发送了会议邀请函，请查收。
EN: I sent a meeting invitation through email, please check.

ZH: 我的邮箱可容纳很大附件，可以发送大文件。
EN: My mailbox can accommodate large attachments and send large files.
